Sentencas: A new series of cobalt-based perovskite (Gd0.6Sr0.4)(0.99)Fe1-xCoxO3-delta (GSFC-x, x = 0.00, 0.05, 0.10, 0.15, 0.20 and 0.25) cathodes to aid in the development of intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells are reported.
Titulo: Thermal properties of (Gd0.6Sr0.4)0.99Fe1-xCoxO3-δ cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: All the perovskites showed the coexistence of cubic and orthorhombic phases.
Titulo: Thermal properties of (Gd0.6Sr0.4)0.99Fe1-xCoxO3-δ cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: To determine their suitability, the thermal properties dependence on the cobalt content were investigated via dilatometry, thermogravimetry and differential scanning calorimetry.
Titulo: Thermal properties of (Gd0.6Sr0.4)0.99Fe1-xCoxO3-δ cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: GSFC-x exhibited the promising activity of the oxygen reduction reaction and ion transport from a comparable study.
Titulo: Thermal properties of (Gd0.6Sr0.4)0.99Fe1-xCoxO3-δ cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The thermal expansion coefficient of rich-cobalt samples showed a more compatible value to the common electrolyte than other similar cathodes.
Titulo: Thermal properties of (Gd0.6Sr0.4)0.99Fe1-xCoxO3-δ cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: By varying Co doping, compromises were made between thermal expansion and electrical conductivity.
Titulo: Thermal properties of (Gd0.6Sr0.4)0.99Fe1-xCoxO3-δ cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
